data.description:
Finally a large house on a large lot meets great condition and an affordable price! Freshly painted inside and out. Hardie board siding. Gorgeous real oak hardwood floors downstairs. 16" tile in the kitchen and baths. Plush carpet in the bedrooms. New septic tank and drainfield. Just tied in to Talquin water. Two new AC units. TONS of natural light. 200 feet of privacy fence. Big bay windows in the master suite. Large walk-in closet and HUGE master bath. You'll love the tiled shower. Classy bronze fixtures throughout. Will install garage for $132,500. Hurry before it's gone!

Brokered And Advertised By: Lord & Stanley Realty, Inc.
Listing Agent: Jason Picht
